				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Bard Epic 1.5 Checklist<a name="69133"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 6 04 10:20 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>(Based on walk thrus provided in this forum. Any mistakes or updates please let me know. Updated 11/16/04)
<br />

<br />
[ ] Have epic 1.0 or have done pre-quest
<br />

<br />
==================
<br />
[ ] <b>Cracked Dragon Bone</b>
<br />
==================
<br />
( ) Talked to Lantaric`Dar in Wakening Lands (optional)
<br />
( ) Kill Mercenaries in Dragon Necropolis
<br />
( ) Kill Excavator (named merc.)
<br />
( ) Kill Tarn Macklin (drops the cracked dragon bone)
<br />

<br />
=====================
<br />
[ ] <b>Blackened Dragon Bones</b>
<br />
=====================
<br />
( ) Hand in Cracked Dragon Bone to Lantaric`Dar (dragon bone returned to you)
<br />
( ) Collect a Dragon Wing Bone, a Dragon Claw Bone, and a Dragon Tail Bone from Dragon Necropolis.
<br />
( ) Turnin all 4 Dragon Bones to Hsagra's Shade in DN (begins a raid level event, final mob drops blackened dragon bones)
<br />

<br />
======
<br />
[ ] <b>Orb</b>
<br />
======
<br />
( ) Hand in Blackened Dragon Bones to Lantaric`Dar
<br />
( ) Kill Vesthan in DN
<br />
( ) Kill Dracolich of Hsadra in DN (spawns on Vesthan's death)
<br />

<br />
=============
<br />
[ ] <b>Draconic Prism</b>
<br />
=============
<br />
( ) Talk to Walthin Fireweaver in the Temple of Ro and recieve a Note. (optional)
<br />
( ) Plains Crystal - Kill A Dire Griffon North Karana / Grey Diamond of Storms
<br />
( ) Forest Crystal - Kill A Dire Kodiak in Jagged Pine / Yellow Diamond of Valor
<br />
( ) Swamp Crystal - Kill A Dire Leech in Swamp of no Hope / Green Diamond of Disease
<br />
( ) Mountain Crystal - Kill A Dire Panda in Stonebrunt / White Diamond of Justice
<br />
( ) Wind Crystal - requires foraged crystal from Skyfire / Cloudy Diamond of Air
<br />
( ) Fire Crystal - requires foraged crystal from Skyfire / Red Diamond of Fire
<br />
( ) Earth Crystal - requires foraged crystal from Skyfire / Brown Diamond of Earth
<br />
( ) Water Crystal - requires foraged crystal from Skyfire / Aqua Diamond of Water
<br />
{The items needed are: Enchanted Bar of Velium + diamondX + crystalX + dragorn blood} 
<br />
-----------------------------------------------------------
<br />
( ) Show the crystals to Walthin Fireweaver
<br />
( ) Hail A Cloaking Figure in Kithicor/ Spawn and kill 4 Malignant Spirits / Kill A Cloaking Figure (loot a Draconic Crest 8 slot container, and a Note from Metala)
<br />
( ) Combine the 8 crystals in the Draconic Crest
<br />

<br />
=====================
<br />
[ ] <b>Rusted Etched Bile Blade</b>
<br />
=====================
<br />
( ) Talk and turin Note from Metala to Vhalen Nostrolo in South Karana (recieve Metala's Necklace)
<br />
( ) Turnin necklace to A Bruised Woman(Metala) in the Plane of Torment and kill her. (loot Rusted Etched Bile Blade 2 slot container)
<br />

<br />
====================
<br />
[ ] <b>Prismatic Dragon Blade</b>
<br />
====================
<br />
( ) Combine the Draconic Prism in the Rusted Etched Bile Blade
<br />
</span></td>
