				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Bard Epic 1.5 Checklist<a name="69863"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 17 04 8:26 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>To make the prisms, you need the following:
<br />

<br />
Using Fire Prism as my example
<br />

<br />
-1 Dragorn Blood 
<br />
-1 Enchanter Velium Bar (Chanter made)
<br />
-1 Red Diamond of Fire (Chanter made w/ Spell:  Imbue Fire, need 1 Raw Diamond and 1 Fire Mephit Blood)
<br />
-1 Fire Dragon Crystal
<br />

<br />
Combine these 4 items in a Jeweler's Kit.
<br />

<br />
Each Prism needs 1 dragorn blood, 1 velium bar, and a crystal, which are either foraged or drop off the dragons.  Each also needs a special diamond, which is chanter made (with 1 EP blood and a raw diamond).
<br />

<br />
Bards do the final combine, they just need chanter made items for subcombines.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
